{"tid":2205502,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國副國務卿周六將會訪問台灣","createTime":"2020-09-17T01:26:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-17T03:33:26.000Z","uid":227801,"like":42,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"2d2ceb8dc87cba283bc2545a05e90f339d759b7e","tid":2205502,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T01:26:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=405847\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D405847&d=WBhgCLuhUD%2FUeH80S3I9%2Bo429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=e81e240b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D405847&h=f3bf229e\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=405847</a><br />\n美國國務院宣布，負責經濟發展、能源及環境事務的克拉奇，將參加周六舉行追悼李登輝的儀式，又稱美國會持續與台灣維繫穩固關係，懷緬李登輝，克拉奇將會是41年來到訪台灣的美國國務院最高級別官員，也是繼美國衞生及公共服務部部長阿扎8月初訪台之後，今年第二位到訪台灣的美國高級官員。<br />\n<br />\n中國外交部發言人早前回應有關報道時表示，中方堅決反對美台官方往來，強調台灣問題事關中國主權和領土完整，涉及中國核心利益，敦促停止一切形式的美台官員往來。"},{"pid":"0ab8b29cc44509a43ed63a0cf06db8feeda8590b","tid":2205502,"uid":321977,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T01:27:08.000Z","msg":"支那:好嬲好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bb38023e6210adb2cd28db6f6da80a17eb7561d","tid":2205502,"uid":227801,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0ab8b29cc44509a43ed63a0cf06db8feeda8590b","tid":2205502,"uid":321977,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T01:27:08.000Z","msg":"支那:好嬲好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T01:29:23.000Z","msg":"輸了<img src=\"/assets/fa